description: Try our easy to follow Tuna Patties + Snacks recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Fish burger,Fish,Zucchini,High fibre,High protein,Fish cake,Tree nut free,Low sugar,Peanut free
name: Tuna Patties + Snacks Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 wholemeal english muffin, halved (for cheese muffin)
0.2 red capsicum, cut into sticks (for capsicum & cucumber sticks)
0.25 continental cucumber, cut into sticks (for capsicum & cucumber sticks)
185g can tuna chunks In springwater, drained, flaked (for tuna patties)
2 tsp extra virgin olive oil (for tuna patties)
2 slice wholemeal soft sandwich bread, made into breadcrumbs (for tuna patties)

recipeInstructions.text: Tuna Patties: Combine the zucchini, tuna, egg and breadcrumbs in a bowl. Season to taste. Shape mixture into 6 patties.

Heat the oil in a large non-stick frying pan over medium heat. Cook patties for 2 minutes each side or until golden brown. Set aside to cool completely. Store in an airtight container in fridge until required.

Pack capsicum & cucumber sticks in an airtight container. Serve with tuna patties. Snack 1: Pack pineapple in an airtight container Snack 2: Top muffin with cheese. Grill until cheese is melted. Cool and cut in half.
